fewer words than people

00:03:23.750 --> 00:03:25.050
who are not born in poverty.

00:03:25.050 --> 00:03:26.410
And we begin to understand

00:03:26.410 --> 00:03:30.050
that despite all the other
obvious economic pressures

00:03:30.050 --> 00:03:34.390
that we have this lasting deficit
that is going to be very difficult

00:03:34.390 --> 00:03:38.420
to make up and I feel so
extraordinarily fortunate

00:03:38.420 --> 00:03:41.400
that not only was I read
to but I've also been able

00:03:41.400 --> 00:03:43.970
to read to my own kids.

00:03:43.970 --> 00:03:47.240
I have four daughters
ranging in many ages

00:03:47.240 --> 00:03:50.480
and I think the intimate
connection I have

00:03:50.480 --> 00:03:52.650
with them has been
foraged over books.

00:03:52.650 --> 00:03:54.820
&gt;&gt; Sam Litzinger: I understand
the family was an influence

00:03:54.820 --> 00:03:57.350
