00:04:00.590 --> 00:04:03.530
about American history, who
tries to define those stories,

00:04:03.530 --> 00:04:07.650
thank you very much for
your generous introduction,

00:04:07.650 --> 00:04:12.670
and when it was time for bed, when
the books were finished reading,

00:04:12.670 --> 00:04:16.490
when the lights were off and I was
either lying next to my daughters

00:04:16.490 --> 00:04:21.360 position:56%
in bed or in a chair next to them, I
