00:08:17.720 --> 00:08:22.330
And then the work was how to tell a
story that didn't make them wrong,

00:08:22.330 --> 00:08:24.740
that made them interesting
and humanized them,

00:08:24.740 --> 00:08:28.870
but also let you know that there
are some very potent issues going

00:08:28.870 --> 00:08:32.970
on in American history about
race, about money, about honesty,

00:08:32.970 --> 00:08:37.320
about all sorts of things and
that's part of the book as well.

00:08:37.320 --> 00:08:39.700
&gt;&gt; Sam Litzinger: Are you
a merciless self editor?

00:08:39.700 --> 00:08:41.780
&gt;&gt; Ken Burns: Yeah, we're
