00:09:04.780 --> 00:09:06.080
&gt;&gt; Sam Litzinger: Do
you love research?

00:09:06.080 --> 00:09:07.380
You must at this point.

00:09:07.380 --> 00:09:08.680
&gt;&gt; Ken Burns: I love it, love it.

00:09:08.680 --> 00:09:11.140 position:56%
I mean I just had the great pleasure
