the smaller detail is more telling.

00:09:53.860 --> 00:09:58.280 position:56%
If you think about it, the
architecture of the atom is the same

00:09:58.280 --> 00:10:00.650
as the architecture
of the solar system.

00:10:00.650 --> 00:10:04.240
So that you could find, as
the poet William Blake said,

00:10:04.240 --> 00:10:06.090
the world in a grain of sand.

00:10:06.090 --> 00:10:09.350 position:56%
And that's what we try to do, to
make something, to personalize it is

00:10:09.350 --> 00:10:11.580
to often go down to
the tale in detail.

00:10:11.580 --> 00:10:16.280 position:56%
So not too far from here is a little
town called Winchester, Virginia.

00:10:16.280 --> 00:10:20.880
It changed hands 72 times
