00:10:31.320 --> 00:10:36.020
that these little nuggets are
also incredibly instructive.

00:10:36.020 --> 00:10:39.920
Humor is also another thing
that is very helpful, you know,

00:10:39.920 --> 00:10:44.880
alligators in bathtubs and
working in your dads saloon

00:10:44.880 --> 00:10:47.980
as Martin Van Buran
did, these are all stuff

00:10:47.980 --> 00:10:50.920
that helps us understand
these complicated people

00:10:50.920 --> 00:10:56.460
that we more often abstract and
make the subject of term papers

00:10:56.460 --> 00:10:59.250
and not the fact that they
